thread.title: Joshua Bell
thread.title_full: TAXIBOX mobile self-storage reviewed by Joshua Bell

author: Joshua Bell
title: Joshua Bell
text: I approached Taxi-Box with very little time to spare and they booked me in at short notice just on the day I needed them. Super helpful and handy, all of my possessions were in perfect condition when they were re-delivered and I was able to access my box during the storage period without trouble.
